# Data Ingestion Pipeline Rules

**Core Philosophy**: Use spaCy-based semantic chunking (300-500 tokens, 20% overlap, 225-450 words).

**Standards**: Clean text, hash docs, upsert to Pinecone, track metrics, test with pytest.

**Scripts**: Use designated scripts per content type (PDF, web, audio/video, DB).
